title: Cyberfunk Juice Bar
description: A charming smoothie/juice bar features a summer garden where you can enjoy fresh juices, smoothies, coffees and teas. Also available are just a few to-go foods. Does not appear to have any vegan smoothies, but the juices are vegan. Internet comes for free with smoothie orders and costs 0.25KN per min with no order. Student discount. Free delivery above 50 KN.
